	src/Makefile.am: android: refresh SDL2 stub and documentation

2017-03-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/IOGfxDisplayGL2.cpp, src/IOGfxGLFuncs.cpp, src/IOGfxGLFuncs.h: 
	GL: fix new issues in snapshot() by explicitely setting the read
	buffer

2017-03-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/Makefile.am: build: declare missing header file

2017-03-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* autobuild/freedink-exe-mxe.sh: autobuild: sdl_mixer->sdl2_mixer

2017-03-28  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* bootstrap, configure.ac, share/Makefile.am: build: mkdir_p is
	obsoleted

2017-03-27  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/TestIOGfxDisplay.cxx: gl: avoid rendering offscreen + make it
	clearer that uploaded surfaces are freed At least one setup (Windows XP + SDL 2.0.5) has specific issues with
	offscreen rendering https://bugzilla.libsdl.org/show_bug.cgi?id=3619
	Since FreeDink does not normally render offscreen, let's avoid
	testing that entirely (even if windows popping-up during tests are
	annoying)

2017-03-27  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/IOGfxDisplayGL2.cpp: gl: pre-concat shader sources to
	anticipate issues with buggy drivers

